 we'll see throughout</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/92172352/image_92172352.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4741547-philip-morris-continues-to-reward-shareholders", "pub_date": "2024-12-02 21:27:25"}, {"id": "4741560", "title": "Is The Concentration Of The Assets Under Custody A Threat For The Global ETF Industry?", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2179071346/image_2179071346.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Assets under management (&lt;a href='https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/AUM' title='Intl Sec Exch ISE Spot AUDUSD Index'&gt;AUM&lt;/a&gt;) is the total market value of the investments that a person or entity manages on behalf of clients\" data-id=\"2179071346\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2179071346/image_2179071346.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2179071346/image_2179071346.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2179071346/image_2179071346.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2179071346/image_2179071346.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2179071346/image_2179071346.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2179071346/image_2179071346.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2179071346/image_2179071346.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2179071346/image_2179071346.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Worawith Ounpeng/iStock via Getty Images</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p><em>By Detlef Glow</em></p> <p>Since the assets under management in the global ETF industry are highly concentrated on different levels (domicile, promoter, classification), it is not surprising that the assets under management are also highly concentrated on the custodial</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2179071346/image_2179071346.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4741560-is-concentration-of-assets-under-custody-threat-for-global-etf-industry", "pub_date": "2024-12-02 21:20:00"}, {"id": "4741544", "title": "TCW Relative Value Mid Cap Fund Q3 2024 Commentary", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1072593728/image_1072593728.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Little piggy banks on ascending stacks of coins\" data-id=\"1072593728\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"5423px\" height=\"3261px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1072593728/image_1072593728.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1072593728/image_1072593728.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1072593728/image_1072593728.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1072593728/image_1072593728.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1072593728/image_1072593728.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1072593728/image_1072593728.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1072593728/image_1072593728.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1072593728/image_1072593728.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">PM Images</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2>Investment Environment</h2> <p>Indices in the U.S. and Europe hit records amid optimism over central bank easing, declining inflation, increasing optimism for a soft landing, and China stimulus. For the first time since 2020, the Federal Reserve (the Fed) cut interest rates doing so by 50</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1072593728/image_1072593728.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4741544-tcw-relative-value-mid-cap-fund-q3-2024-commentary", "pub_date": "2024-12-02 21:12:00"}, {"id": "4741551", "title": "Will Stocks Continue To Rhyme With 2016?", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2159126735/image_2159126735.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"A double exposure image of skyscrapers with overlay of financial graphs, set against a blurred background, illustrating the concept of business growth\" data-id=\"2159126735\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2159126735/image_2159126735.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2159126735/image_2159126735.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2159126735/image_2159126735.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2159126735/image_2159126735.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2159126735/image_2159126735.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2159126735/image_2159126735.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2159126735/image_2159126735.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2159126735/image_2159126735.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">peshkov</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p><em>By Geoff Bysshe</em></p> <p></p> <p>From everyone at MarketGauge, we hope you\u2019ve had an enjoyable Thanksgiving weekend and that it kicks off a happy and healthy holiday season for you and the ones you love.</p> <p>November closed with the distinction</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2159126735/image_2159126735.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4741551-will-stocks-continue-to-rhyme-with-2016", "pub_date": "2024-12-02 21:05:00"}, {"id": "4741536", "title": "DHL: Tariffs Pose Risks, But Expected Return Of Over 10% Makes It Compelling", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2156421322/image_2156421322.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"DHL Boeing 767 Take Off\" data-id=\"2156421322\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1025px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2156421322/image_2156421322.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2156421322/image_2156421322.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2156421322/image_2156421322.