"pub_date": "2024-12-02 20:32:35"}, {"id": "4741546", "title": "OPEC Update - November 2024", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1455527715/image_1455527715.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Low Wide Angle Image of an Off-Shore Oil Rig at Dusk Off the Coast of Huntington Beach with Copy Space\" data-id=\"1455527715\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1455527715/image_1455527715.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1455527715/image_1455527715.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1455527715/image_1455527715.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1455527715/image_1455527715.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1455527715/image_1455527715.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1455527715/image_1455527715.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1455527715/image_1455527715.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1455527715/image_1455527715.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Jeremy Poland</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p><em>By D. Coyne</em></p> <p>The <a href=\"https://www.opec.org/opec_web/en/publications/338.htm\" rel=\"nofollow\">OPEC Monthly Oil Market Report</a> (MOMR) for November 2024 was published recently. The last month reported in most of the OPEC c